On the Tuesday edition of the Alex Jones Show, Alex welcomes back critically acclaimed author and former State Department official Steve Pieczenik. Steve talks with Alex about the ongoing Iran assassination and terror plot drama now being used by the U.S. government to drive the country into a catastrophic war that will ignite the Middle East. 

Alex also covers the latest breaking news and talks about the undermining of the Occupy Wall Street movement by socialists and Marxists, efforts by the Federal Reserve to censor Infowars at YouTube, and other important topics of the day.
